<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zxx">

<head>
	<title>Traversal Hesap Oluştur</title>
	<!-- Meta tag Keywords -->
	<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
	<meta charset="UTF-8" />
	<meta name="keywords"
		content="Invent Signup Form Responsive web template, Bootstrap Web Templates, Flat Web Templates, Android Compatible web template, Smartphone Compatible web template, free webdesigns for Nokia, Samsung, LG, SonyEricsson, Motorola web design" />
	<script>
		addEventListener("load", function () {
			setTimeout(hideURLbar, 0);
		}, false);

		function hideURLbar() {
			window.scrollTo(0, 1);
		}
	</script>
	<!-- //Meta tag Keywords -->
	<!--/Style-CSS -->
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="~/Web/css/style.css" type="text/css" media="all" />
	<!--//Style-CSS -->
</head>

<body>
	<!-- /login-section -->
	<section class="w3l-login-6">
		<div class="login-hny">
			<div class="form-content">
				<div class="form-right">
					<div class="overlay">
						<div class="grid-info-form">
							<h5>Say hello</h5>
							<h3>Hesap Oluştur </h3>
							<p>Bize katılarak dünyayı keşfetmenin ilk adımını atın. Üyelik ile size özel fırsatları,
								güncel kampanyaları ve kişiselleştirilmiş seyahat önerilerini kaçırmayın. 
								Hem güvenli hem de keyifli bir seyahat deneyimi için hemen kayıt olun!</p>
							<a href="index.html" class="read-more-1 btn">Get Started</a>
						</div>
					
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="form-left">
					<div class="middle">
						<h4>Bize Katılın</h4>
						<p>Hemen Hesap Oluşturn Hem de Ücretsiz.</p>
					</div>
					<form  method="post" class="signin-form">
							<div class="form-input">
								<label>Adınız</label>
								<input type="text"  placeholder="" asp-for="Name" />
								<span asp-validation-for="Name" style="color:red"></span>
							</div>
							<div class="form-input">
								<label>Soydınız</label>
								<input type="text"  placeholder="" asp-for="Surname" />
							<span asp-validation-for="Surname" style="color:red"></span>

							</div>
							<div class="form-input">
								<label>Kullanızı Adınız</label>
								<input type="text"  placeholder="" asp-for="UserName" />
							<span asp-validation-for="UserName" style="color:red"></span>

							</div>
							<div class="form-input">
								<label>Email</label>
								<input type="email"  placeholder="" asp-for="Mail" />
							<span asp-validation-for="Mail" style="color:red"></span>

							</div>
							<div class="form-input">
								<label>Şifre</label>
								<input type="password" placeholder="" asp-for="Password" />
							<span asp-validation-for="Password" style="color:red"></span>
							<div style="color:aqua" asp-validation-summary="ModelOnly">

							</div>
							<div class="form-input">
								<label>Şifre Tekrar</label>
							<input type="password"  placeholder="" asp-for="ConfirmPassword" />
							<span asp-validation-for="ConfirmPassword" style="color:red"></span>

							</div>
							<label class="container">I agree to <a href="#">Conditions</a> Okudum Kabul Ediyorum <a href="#">Privacy</a>
								<input type="checkbox">
								<span class="checkmark"></span>
							</label>
							<button class="btn">Hesap Oluştur</button>
					</form>
					<div class="copy-right text-center">
						<p>© @DateTime.Now.Year Invent Signup. All rights reserved | Design by
								<a href="http://w3layouts.com/" target="_blank">W3layouts</a></p>
					 </div>
				</div>
				
			</div>
			
		</div>
	</section>
	<!-- //login-section -->
</body>

</html>